    Verse: 21
Tags:
  - Enthusiasm
---
Enthusiasm is the thing which makes the world go round. Without its driving
power, nothing worth doing has ever been done. Love, friendship, religion,
altruism, devotion to career or hobby, -- all these, and most of the other
good things of life, are forms of enthusiasm.
